Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.92,0:01:04.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,A書被女朋友找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.23,0:01:06.66,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,關鍵還是歐美
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.90,0:01:07.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,香…香奈同學!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.02,0:01:10.09,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,今天是來考前複習的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.09,0:01:11.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,學個鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.52,0:01:14.25,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,反正千秋只會想這些事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.27,0:01:16.11,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,才 才沒有這樣的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.16,0:01:17.75,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那 那麼想做的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.80,0:01:18.93,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,做不就好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.94,0:01:25.07,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這 這種事情不是要再深一步的時候嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.07,0:01:27.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是千秋你什麼也沒做不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.28,0:01:28.64,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,連接吻也還沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.69,0:01:30.86,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這還不是因為你現在沒給人這種氛…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.86,0:01:32.20,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,小伙子 怕了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.18,0:01:34.45,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,吾 吾之名為千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:36.25,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,乃榮耀的恩恵之子與孝之子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.38,0:01:38.78,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那還不滾過來 不然把你頭轉下來!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.70,0:01:41.73,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那…那
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.61,0:01:50.44,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,香奈 意外的胸挺大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.47,0:01:52.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,超想揉 可以的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.14,0:01:53.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,好勒 上了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.61,0:01:57.77,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦 接吻什麼還…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.07,0:01:58.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊不 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.76,0:02:00.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,剛剛的不算 不要在意!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.16,0:02:02.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不行不行不行 按順序 順序
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.29,0:02:04.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,大家在這種時候都怎麼弄得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.62,0:02:06.32,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是總先從接吻開始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.15,0:02:08.95,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 我的嘴裡會不會臭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:10.65,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嘴唇也可能太乾燥了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.02,0:02:12.44,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,說到底我一身汗真的不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.45,0:02:14.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,今天內褲穿的什麼樣式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.04,0:02:15.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 屁要是放出來了怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.88,0:02:17.41,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,乳頭的毛要是早點拔…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.56,0:02:18.32,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 大便
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.84,0:02:21.36,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,剛剛不是去過了嗎 你在逃避什麼啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.36,0:02:23.55,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 不是的 想稍微準備一下什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.55,0:02:26.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,而且你對這種事情又不喜歡太急
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.06,0:02:29.35,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,「接吻了就是戀人了」這種話我也不想聽…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.59,0:02:35.27,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,香 香奈同學!? 女孩子不應該突然暴露裸體的唷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:36.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,囉嗦 笨蛋千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.49,0:02:38.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,就算是我也不是只是著急想要接吻什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.92,0:02:41.39,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎麼說 只是想要變得更加在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.41,0:02:43.52,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以想要更了解千秋什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.56,0:02:45.67,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你也想要更了解我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.70,0:02:46.26,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,香奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:47.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,別看!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:47.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,好狠!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.82,0:02:49.83,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,還說什麼想更了解我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.83,0:02:51.07,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,煩死了 色情千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.07,0:02:52.23,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,把燈關了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.18,0:02:56.28,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,話說在前面 我的身材並不是很好來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.58,0:02:59.63,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,還有今天沒時間洗澡所以汗什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.16,0:03:01.58,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是剛剛稍微看到了一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.59,0:03:02.51,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,超美的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.77,0:03:06.36,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,笨蛋千秋 屎千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.54,0:03:05.17,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}明明在誇你 明明在誇你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.80,0:03:09.60,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是 我完全沒準備這種時候的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.47,0:03:12.32,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒 沒關係的啦這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.43,0:03:15.40,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,才不是沒關係啊 我去買回來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:20.41,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不是 今天出門的時候我媽說 要我拿著…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:24.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那 也就是說已經準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.31,0:03:25.79,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,喂 千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:27.12,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.44,0:03:28.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.01,0:03:30.51,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我也喜歡你 香奈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.03,0:03:34.92,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,吶千秋 快給香奈些點心…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:36.95,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哎呀 真是失敬了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.10,0:03:39.58,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,點心放這了 完事之後要吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:42.85,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,千秋他姐姐 不可以上二樓唷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.34,0:03:44.29,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.48,0:03:47.02,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒事 我家也像這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.76,0:03:49.01,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那繼續做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.27,0:03:52.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:56.01,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,有好好做避孕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.02,0:03:57.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我的借給你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:58.55,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,老媽!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.21,0:04:04.25,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,被學生會長看到抽菸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.54,0:04:05.57,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,還被表白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:08.86,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,而且作為條件居然還要我戒菸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.25,0:04:11.24,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.21,0:04:15.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,阿勒 我幹嘛老實戒菸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:20.73,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,話說不是沒說過要和我交往這種話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.02,0:04:23.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 梶同學 把我叫到這種地方有什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.96,0:04:26.20,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,赤木 我有話要跟你說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.21,0:04:28.02,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你不就是抓著我的弱點…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.06,0:04:30.36,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,弱點? 一被表揚就很害羞之類的?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:34.23,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,才不是! 抽菸的事啊 而且你也沒說交往的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:36.07,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,喔～ 那我再…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.09,0:04:36.99,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,別用你說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:38.83,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,就接吻了一次就覺得自己是男朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:39.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,做了兩次喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.04,0:04:40.80,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,囉嗦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:43.59,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,又不是第一次接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:46.25,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這樣就想攻陷女生…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:48.40,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那你想要怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.86,0:04:52.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,都說了 為什麼對我…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:54.80,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,更愛一點? 真是拿你沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.09,0:04:55.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.86,0:04:57.25,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,來個鬼啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:04:59.82,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,說到底你根本沒喜歡我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:01.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒有這回事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.08,0:05:04.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,騙人 明明對我什麼都不了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:06.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯 確實不是很了解呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.01,0:05:08.63,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你看 果然是這…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.63,0:05:10.31,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,除了在學校看到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.23,0:05:12.81,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒有什麼朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.97,0:05:14.98,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,上課時 也一直睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.28,0:05:18.65,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,明明可以早點回家卻在這抽菸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:23.17,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,上次並不是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.70,0:05:25.13,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,之前就對你有興趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:28.10,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以你覺得表白了我就一定會答應嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:28.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:32.36,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我覺得梶同學 是那種只要被表白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:34.18,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,就絕對不會拒絕的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:36.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你看 實際上就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.04,0:05:38.75,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以完全沒辦法放心把你交給輕浮的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.26,0:05:42.86,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嘛 作為我喜歡的人你肉還少了點就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.97,0:05:45.33,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,果然呢 說得好聽是個學生會長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.33,0:05:47.36,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,其實腦袋裡就只有些色色的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:50.21,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,確實如果能和梶同學一起睡的話我也想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.78,0:05:52.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.07,0:05:53.30,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那這樣的話現在就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:56.28,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以在你被其他男人搶走之前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.47,0:05:58.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我要先霸占你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:06:00.82,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你從剛才開始都在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.14,0:06:03.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,都說了讓梶同學成為我的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:04.18,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真煩人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.56,0:06:08.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,因為你啊 像我這樣的傢伙 為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.28,0:06:09.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,大概 因為喜歡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:15.26,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,大概是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.69,0:06:16.81,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我也搞不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.19,0:06:19.01,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我也沒有喜歡過別人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:22.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是如果這都不是戀愛那什麼是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:23.63,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我怎麼知道這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.66,0:06:24.79,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,試著弄明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.27,0:06:27.24,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,當然前提是你覺得沒問題的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.13,0:06:29.54,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不會勉強或是強迫你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.71,0:06:35.67,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.97,0:06:38.67,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 要交往嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:42.19,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 那個 但是 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.37,0:06:43.18,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.43,0:06:45.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 都說了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.81,0:06:49.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,說「嗯」就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:50.43,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.94,0:06:57.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,之前我被皆川同學表白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.40,0:07:01.52,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是拖了好幾個月都沒有給她答覆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.60,0:07:08.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,到這時候再不答覆她的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.48,0:07:16.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,吶 古屋君 我已經等好久啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:18.40,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,差不多該告訴我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.46,0:07:20.63,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這 這個話題過下兩個人的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.63,0:07:21.35,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,Line怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.82,0:07:25.17,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那現在 我能收到結果嘛～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.64,0:07:28.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,皆川你啊 到底是在玩還是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.15,0:07:29.30,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我判斷不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:32.45,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉 那我這次一定好好聽著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.00,0:07:33.75,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎麼說?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:36.02,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:37.82,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,交…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.82,0:07:39.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,交往不了吶?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.24,0:07:41.95,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我知道了 如果古屋君你沒有這個想法的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.03,0:07:45.01,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊不 那個 也不是沒有那個想法…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.01,0:07:46.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,一提到要給答覆了… 我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.87,0:07:50.53,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,其實我才是不明白古屋君到底是在玩還是認真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:51.79,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那個 我不是這…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.79,0:07:52.29,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.96,0:07:53.80,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.07,0:07:56.03,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,馬上也要上課了 拜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.39,0:07:58.94,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦… 咦咦咦咦咦咦!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.31,0:08:01.63,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒想到 居然這麼乾脆的放棄了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:02.57,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不對 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.64,0:08:04.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這其實也是皆川同學在演戲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:06.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,其實在等我阻止她不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.52,0:08:09.36,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,傻嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.73,0:08:12.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,到底還是我不對啊 讓她等了那麼久
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:14.45,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,總而言之過下再聊一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:17.02,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,就算是皆川同學也多少會有些青澀的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.52,0:08:23.17,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不對啊這… 這不是放棄了而是心冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.42,0:08:26.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這也難怪啊 我這麼優柔寡斷的傢伙…
