Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:31.85,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦!? 為什麼會知道啊!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:33.95,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,說起來 皆川同學不是在生氣嗎?
