Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.97,0:08:41.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,就是突然想調戲你一下。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:43.54,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,再者現在也沒有很急著想要答覆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:45.99,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,還有…
