Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.46,0:08:49.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,果然還是不說好啦（笑）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:53.20,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.77,0:08:56.61,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,他在認真關注我～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.42,0:09:00.48,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,被朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:03.39,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,拜託幫忙送情書了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:05.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,要送的人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.24,0:09:07.23,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,菅原君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:07.93,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:12.30,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,考試期間還打擾你抱歉 有話和你說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:13.90,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,放學後方便嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.64,0:09:16.29,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,方便 完全方便
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.77,0:09:17.97,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,只要是高野的請求…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.11,0:09:19.85,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,果然是個好人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.57,0:09:22.18,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,信!? 給我!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.39,0:09:22.92,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.63,0:09:27.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,謝…謝謝 沒想到高野能給我這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:29.71,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不是喔 這個是吉永同學給的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.52,0:09:33.81,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這 這樣啊 好不好意思呢 哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.16,0:09:37.38,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,然後那個… 可以的話她希望能聽到你的答覆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.55,0:09:42.75,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,別太在意哈 這個時候最費神的畢竟是高野你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.96,0:09:45.61,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,菅原君你啊 真的是一個好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:50.60,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,能幫我告訴吉永同學「對不起」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:52.77,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,因為我也有喜歡的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:56.55,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 不表白嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.13,0:09:58.65,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,姑且是 表過白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.04,0:10:01.61,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,對方完全沒有意識到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.75,0:10:04.43,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這種事情也有的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:06.65,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不再表白一次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:10.83,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不了吧… 因為我對於那個人而言只是個好人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.52,0:10:13.64,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這個人和我很像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.11,0:10:17.54,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那 高野你的話 要是被我表白了準備怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:19.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不可能的啦真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.69,0:10:23.83,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我對這種事情不太了解 和我交往也很無趣的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.17,0:10:26.54,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,感覺我喜歡的人也會這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.61,0:10:28.90,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 感覺好麻煩的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:30.22,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真是該怎麼辦才好呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.74,0:10:33.39,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,稍微強勢一點說不定好一些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:36.77,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,試著抱上去之類的 電視劇裡不也很常見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.92,0:10:39.56,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那種會抱上去說「喜歡你啊」一類的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.98,0:10:42.91,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這 這種事情要是高野你被人這樣不會很困擾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.04,0:10:45.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,肯定困擾啊 會掙脫的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:45.89,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:48.52,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是 因為菅原君你是個好人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.69,0:10:50.31,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,如果是我的話會原諒你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.07,0:10:53.22,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,能作為參考嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.03,0:10:56.29,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,差不多該回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:10:59.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,走吧 還得考前複習
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:02.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,也 也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:21.12,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我啊 已經放棄表白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.17,0:11:22.24,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦? 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.42,0:11:25.42,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,向無法成為戀愛對象的人表白只是徒增對方煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.91,0:11:28.45,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,高野你也是 被我表白了也只是會很困擾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:32.23,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是菅原你喜歡的人和我不一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:35.18,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,高野要是說很困擾的話 大概不成吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:37.35,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我 說了多餘了話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.58,0:11:39.92,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不不 非常有參考價值
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.12,0:11:42.30,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 關於吉永那邊的答覆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:44.45,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我明天親口向她說「對不起」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:45.26,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒關係嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.62,0:11:49.65,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,雖然她是通過別人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:51.94,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但我還是想好好回應那份告白的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.20,0:12:00.80,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那麼 考試加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:09.52,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,菅原君你 這麼溫柔真的是個好人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:12.66,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,要是向我表白…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.15,0:12:13.98,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,喜歡你!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.77,0:12:24.42,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,雖然 這種事情是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:29.26,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,下回 在遠方望著你
